{
  "stem": "4700.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they both studied economics and industrial relations.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My elder son lectures at Griffith University in Queensland, in industrial relations and labor history.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And my younger son works in a firm, which does environmental impact studies.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he is very active in council, environmental matters, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we are very happy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They've got lovely girls, lovely wives.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And our elder son has got two boys.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my younger son, one boy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And do you think that your experiences during the war and Theresienstadt affected your personality--",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, definitely, definitely.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I feel that things don't worry me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't worry about little things.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But now always, when my husband was worried, I said, is it a matter of life and death?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If it isn't, why are you worried?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sort of you, you know what's important and what isn't important.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I didn't worry when I went for a job interview.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because, well, either I get the job, or I don't get the job, but-- and also human relations became very precious for me, and family, of course.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because our family was so sadly decimated, so--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, well, my aunt was married to a non-Jew, so that family survived.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my two cousins were in England, so they survived.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the rest, was, everybody was-- nobody came back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Everybody was killed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I used to feel very guilty about it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We all did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because, because we just felt that somehow it wasn't fair.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Why should I survive and not the others, who were, perhaps, so much more talented and had so much more to give?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Also I used to feel guilty for not having been to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because Theresienstadt wasn't half as bad as the extermination camps.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And of course, you get over it  in time.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
